## STORY 1 --OneTrust to IH
Title - Publish Consent Update Event

Description
As an integration platform, I want consent changes published as events, So that downstream systems receive updates in real time.
Acceptance Criteria
Consent update event is triggered
Event payload contains mandatory fields
Duplicate events are prevented
Retry mechanism exists
Failed events move to DLQ

## STORY 2 --IH to SFMC
Title -Synchronize Marketing Consent Status

Description
As a marketing platform, I want latest consent status synced, So that only eligible customers receive communications.
Acceptance Criteria
Consent status updates successfully
Opt-out customers are suppressed
Sync occurs within SLA
Error logs are maintained
